{"tid":2248212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太靠近發情鹿群 英國正妹差點被「老漢推車」","createTime":"2020-10-18T12:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T00:53:19.000Z","uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e192a98b012ab306fa8f0429c0125ee24f8268f","tid":2248212,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.allusanewshub.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/woman-attacked-by-wild-deer-in-richmond-park-while-posing-for-instagram-2048x1346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.allusanewshub.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fwoman-attacked-by-wild-deer-in-richmond-park-while-posing-for-instagram-2048x1346.jpg&h=b9c62568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國1名正妹在倫敦的皇家園林「里奇蒙公園（Richmond Park）」遊玩，由於在餵鹿時太靠近鹿隻，差點出現被「老漢推車」的狀況，園方連忙呼籲民眾在鹿群發情期間最好保持距離。<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，英國皇家公園警察（Royal Parks Police）在推特上發布了1張照片，只見穿著蔚藍色洋裝的女子站在田野當中，1頭鹿則從後方伸起前腳頂住她的臀部，似乎正在用力推著她。雖然皇家公園警察隨後刪除了照片，但早已在社群網站廣為流傳。<br />\n<br />\n里奇蒙公園主管理查茲（Simon Richards）向《福斯新聞》證實，這名女性當時正在餵食鹿群，由於太靠近了最後被鹿隻「跳到身上」，幸好她沒有受到嚴重的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n理查茲說，這起意外正好向民眾說明，鹿仍然是充滿野性且不可預測的動物，遊客最好跟牠們保持50公尺的距離，尤其是目前正處於發情期，雄鹿充滿著睪固酮和腎上腺素。<br />\n<br />\n理查茲還表示，其實以鹿群著稱的里奇蒙公園和灌木公園（Bushy Park）已提供充足的天然食物，民眾私下餵食對於鹿隻健康的壞處大過於好處，而且會讓自己陷入不必要的危險當中。據了解，里奇蒙公園與灌木公園有1000多頭自由放養的鹿隻。<br />\n<br />\n英國皇家花園（The Royal Parks）更警告，里奇蒙公園和灌木公園的鹿群在發情期間，1隻鹿就重達350磅（約158.7公斤）以上並且鹿角相當尖銳，被時速48公里的雄鹿撞上跟被機車撞擊沒什麼兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，過去早就發生民眾被鹿隻襲擊的意外，2018年，1名年輕女子在灌木公園因為太靠近發情雄鹿拍照結果受傷；更早1年在里奇蒙公園也有遊客被雄鹿頂傷住院，幾乎所有事故都沒有保持50公尺的安全距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3324816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3324816&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=99f696e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3324816&h=92e0b518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3324816</a>"},{"pid":"5d582cbce220fef6570b9d2c4bae5a3c4a5c3d94","tid":2248212,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e596e3bed3973094f4b0600e8f39cf87c43a43","tid":2248212,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"人獸交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705757ce39cf0a595b4edef30efbbffe44ee1d70","tid":2248212,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"無樣睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/10/18/NZ34iP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F10%2F18%2FNZ34iP.png&h=eade203c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b585bae670d5116e59657d5fa1cd6386ff116d8e","tid":2248212,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"乜動物會對其他物種有性趣架咩<br />\n仲以為只會對自己物種既異性有反應"},{"pid":"3876f1007d3c9695a8380c4201e39dace7183e9e","tid":2248212,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2e7ae64bcfe0731a0aadb7419346716dcbec84","tid":2248212,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"隻鹿無角架喎，點推車呀"}]}